block.name: TagString
block.info: Whether it's a red button, volcano, avian bird flu, meteor, cosmic superhighway or economic collapse, this lecture will give you the information you need to make things that will increase your chances of survival. This lecture will present a broad array of projects that will be both practical and humorous. Some projects are projects that I have made and will have on hand to demonstrate including a diy water purifier and steam-engine powered battery charger. I'll also point the way to over the top projects like making an EMP Generator to deal with the robot uprising. /
block.data: Whether it's a red button, volcano, avian bird flu, meteor, cosmic superhighway or economic collapse, this lecture will give you the information you need to make things that will increase your chances of survival. This lecture will present a broad array of projects that will be both practical and humorous. Some projects are projects that I have made and will have on hand to demonstrate including a diy water purifier and steam-engine powered battery charger. I'll also point the way to over the top projects like making an EMP Generator to deal with the robot uprising.
